# Web UI patterns

- **Theme:** CSS variables in `web/frontend/index.html` `:root` (e.g. `--bg-page`, `--bg-card`, `--border`, `--sky` / `--green` / `--amber` / `--red`) plus any overrides in `app.js` — do not reference deleted `ui/theme.py` (colors are inlined in Python only where noted in `core/alerts.py` / `analysis/thresholds.py`).
- **Threading:** only the FastAPI/WebSocket thread mutates shared backend state; frontend is event-driven DOM updates.
- **Charts:** RSSI — canvas + `requestAnimationFrame`; ping — Chart.js with `animation: false`.
